'''2013年Mi-8直升機墜毀於雅庫次克事件'''是指在2013年7月2日時，一架隸屬{{Link-en|極地航空|Polar Airlines}}的[[Mi-8直升機|Mi-8直升機]]在[[薩哈共和國|薩哈共和國]][[雅庫次克|雅庫次克]]附近山區墜毀<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.interfax.ru/russia/txt.asp?id=316260 |title= В катастрофе Ми-8 выжили четверо |author=  |date= 2013-07-03 |publisher= [[國際文傳電訊社|國際文傳電訊社]] |language=  |accessdate= 2013-07-05 |quote=  |archive-date= 2013-10-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131027074939/http://interfax.ru/russia/txt.asp?id=316260 |dead-url= no }}{{ru}}</ref>。目前確認直升機上墜毀時載有共25名乘客，其中包括11名兒童，另外還有3名機組人員也在直升機上<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://rt.com/news/helicopter-chopper-crash-dead-521/ |title= Kids feared among 21 dead in Siberia copter crash |author=  |date= 2013-07-02 |publisher= [[今日俄羅斯|今日俄羅斯]] |language= en |accessdate= 2013-07-05 |quote=  |archive-date= 2020-06-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200608005040/https://www.rt.com/news/helicopter-chopper-crash-dead-521/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-23142651 |title= Children die in air crash in Russia's Sakha Republic |author=  |date= 2013-07-02 |publisher= [[BBC新聞|BBC新聞]] |language= en |accessdate= 2013-07-05 |quote=  |archive-date= 2020-11-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201111212334/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-23142651 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/07/02/us-russia-helicopter-crash-idUSBRE96107O20130702 |title= Russian helicopter crash kills at least 19 |author= Steve Gutterman |date= 2013-07-02 |publisher= [[路透社|路透社]] |language= en |accessdate= 2013-07-05 |quote=  |archive-date= 2015-09-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150924182642/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/07/02/us-russia-helicopter-crash-idUSBRE96107O20130702 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。而根據地方官員最早表示這次直升機墜毀造成機上23人死亡，並且在死亡名單中還包括1名兒童<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.itar-tass.com/en/c32/792754.html |title= 23 die in Yakutia helicopter crash, 5 survive |author=  |date= 2013-07-02 |publisher= [[俄通社-塔斯社|俄通社-塔斯社]] |language= en |accessdate= 2013-07-05 |quote=  |archive-date= 2013-09-21 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054841/http://www.itar-tass.com/en/c32/792754.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>；而之後死亡人數則追加至24人，並且將生還者訊息更新為3名機組人員與1名12歲男童<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://www.newsru.com/russia/03jul2013/vert2.html |title= Упавший в Якутии Ми-8 найден: спаслись четверо, в том числе сильно травмированный ребенок. 24 погибли |author=  |date= 2013-07-03 |publisher= {{Link-en|NEWSru|NEWSru}} |language= en |accessdate= 2013-07-05 |quote=  |archive-date= 2019-04-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190422034829/https://www.newsru.com/russia/03jul2013/vert2.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。初步的分析報告認為直升機是因為遭遇強風而墜毀，而[[俄羅斯州際航空委員會|俄羅斯州際航空委員會]]正在對於墜毀一事展開更進一步的調查<ref>{{Cite web |url= http://en.ria.ru/russia/20130702/182003060/At-least-15-Killed-in-Siberian-Helicopter-Crash---Police.html |title= Helicopter Crash in Siberia Kills at Least 19 - Officials |author=  |date= 2013-07-02 |publisher= [[俄羅斯新聞社|俄羅斯新聞社]] |language= en |accessdate= 2013-07-05 |quote=  |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130710202735/http://en.ria.ru/russia/20130702/182003060/At-least-15-Killed-in-Siberian-Helicopter-Crash---Police.html |archivedate= 2013-07-10 }}</ref>。

